    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<AircraftState>, java.util.Collection<AircraftState>, java.util.List<AircraftState>, java.util.RandomAccess

    public class Track
extends java.util.ArrayList<AircraftState>
    Created by luke on 7/04/16. Represents a continuous track of an aircraft as it flies through the air, with regular TrackEntry's representing the state of the aircraft for each point in time.
